---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/mainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout lang="sr" title="Magnet And Care">
	<section class="relative flex justify-center py-24 bg-cover bg-fixed bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('/hand_hero.jpg');">
		<div class="relative z-10 lg:w-4/5 flex  items-center">
			<div class="w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4">
				<h1 class="font-bold text-4xl mb-6">Dobrodošli u <span class="gradient-text">Magnet And Care</span> DOO</h1>
				<p class="text-2xl">
					Naša misija je pružanje vrhunske nege starijim i invalidnim osobama, omogućavajući im dostojanstven i kvalitetan život. </br>
					Sa sedištem u Apatinu, Srbija, naš tim stručnjaka svakodnevno radi na poboljšanju života onih kojima je potrebna podrška. </br>
					Mi brinemo o vašim najmilijima, pružajući im sveobuhvatnu negu i pažnju koju zaslužuju.
				</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4">
					<a href="/about" class="inline-block py-2 px-4 rounded-lg bg-accent font-bold text-lg">Saznaj više o nama</a>
					<a href="/contact" class="inline-block py-2 px-4 rounded-lg bg-primary md:hover:bg-accent duration-300 font-bold text-lg text-background md:hover:text-text">Kontaktiraj nas</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="w-1/2 flex justify-center">
				<img src="/mc_logo.svg" alt="Logo" class="w-72">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="absolute z-0 top-0 w-full h-full bg-white/80"></div>
	</section>
	<section class="flex justify-center">
		<div class="w-4/5 py-24 flex justify-center gap-16">
			<div class="relative w-340 flex flex-col flex-nowrap border-4 border-accent rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="absolute -top-6 -left-1 py-1 pr-2 bg-background text-2xl">Radno vreme</h2>
				<div class="m-8 flex flex-col gap-5">
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Ponedeljak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Utorak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Sreda</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Četvrtak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Petak</span>
						<span>08:30 - 16:30</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Subota</span>
						<span class="text-red-600">ZATVORENO</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span>Nedelja</span>
						<span class="text-red-600">ZATVORENO</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative w-340 flex flex-col flex-nowrap border-4 border-accent rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="absolute -top-6 -left-1 py-1 pr-2 bg-background text-2xl">Hitni kontakt</h2>
				<div class="m-8">
					<a href="tel:+38164118894" class="flex justify-between mb-4 p-4 bg-accent md:hover:bg-primary md:hover:text-background duration-300 rounded-full font-semibold text-2xl">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-8"><title>phone-alert</title><path d="M6.62,10.79C8.06,13.62 10.38,15.94 13.21,17.38L15.41,15.18C15.69,14.9 16.08,14.82 16.43,14.93C17.55,15.3 18.75,15.5 20,15.5A1,1 0 0,1 21,16.5V20A1,1 0 0,1 20,21A17,17 0 0,1 3,4C3,3.44 3.45,3 4,3H7.5A1,1 0 0,1 8.5,4C8.5,5.24 8.7,6.45 9.07,7.57C9.18,7.92 9.1,8.31 8.82,8.58L6.62,10.79M17,12V10H19V12H17M17,8V2H19V8H17Z" /></svg>
						<div>+381-64-118894</div>
					</a>
					<p>
						Ako vam je potreban hitan kontakt, pozovite nas i neko će vam se javiti u najkraćem mogućem roku tokom radnog vremena. </br>
						Vaša briga nam je prioritet, a naš tim je tu da pruži podršku kada vam je najpotrebnija.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative w-340 flex flex-col flex-nowrap border-4 border-accent rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="absolute -top-6 -left-1 py-1 pr-2 bg-background text-2xl">Pružamo vam</h2>
				<div class="m-8 flex flex-col gap-1.5">
					<span>&bull; Kvalitetnu medicinsku negu</span>
					<span>&bull; Posvećenu zdravstvenu uslugu</span>
					<span>&bull; Besplatan smeštaj za zaposlene</span>
					<span>&bull; Besplatna ishrana za zaposlene</span>
					<span>&bull; Obezbeđene radne vize</span>
					<span>&bull; Plaćen i organizovan prevoz</span>
					<span>&bull; Osiguran privremeni boravak</span>
					<span>&bull; Stalni radni odnos</span>
					<span>&bull; Isplatu zarade na tekući račun</span>
					<span>&bull; Uplatu poreza i doprinosa</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section>
		<div class="h-[2000px]"></div>
	</section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
.gradient-text {
	background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(13, 124, 131), rgb(95, 221, 230));
	-webkit-background-clip: text;
	-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	background-clip: text;
	text-fill-color: transparent;
}

</style>